      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "先程の、新車のショールームに引き続き\n今度は、中古車メインの展示場にやって来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.146226909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9733787578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "街中ではあまり見かけないような、変わった車や\n前のオーナーさんがカスタムしたらしい車も多いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0666665912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ではこちらも、順番に見ていきたいと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8143312177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.2009980083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "こちらの展示場は、昔の映画で観たような……と言うか\nクラシックな車が多いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.033333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5825176915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ。あの車、ドアが上に向かって開くんですね\nまるで、車から羽が生えたみたいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9000000517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4625179013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ガルウィングですね。見た目のインパクトだけじゃなく\n日本の狭い駐車場では、案外便利なんだそうで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.233333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……\nあら、あちらにも変わった車がありますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5000000517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1891847492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "三輪の、車とバイクを足して二で割ったような……\nあれもちゃんと公道を走れるのでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.733333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4446720641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "トライクですね。……どれもめずらしい車ですけど\n気になったものはありましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9666667183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……例の、外車のCMのせいか\nドリフト走行がどうこうと話を振られることも多いので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.033333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.8525409262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "いっそ、それが得意な車にするのもアリですね\nタイヤを斜めにセッティングしてあるのが、それかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2192071001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.395874393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、マフラーも派手な方が目を引きそうだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.395874393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさん、今まで車には興味なかったらしいけど）\n（車のセンスがなんというか、こう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4666723132,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6699.994353500003,
          "startTime": 99.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.8014352839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "あちらに展示している車も、見に行きましょうか\n……あら？　誰か近づいてきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0746338777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.9497826751
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "ここのディーラーの方かしら\nどちら様でしょう。私達に、何かご用でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9497826751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "……あぁ、こちらの展示場の方でしたか\n撮影許可はいただいたのですが、うるさくてすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2333379626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5544487993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "……え、違う？　個性的な車を探しているなら\n私が絶対に気に入る、うってつけの一台がある、と？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.91675153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっとmihoさん\nなんか怪しいですし、ついて行くのは少し待った方が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5503852601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4347206791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "分かっていない人ですね\nそれならそれで、いい動画のネタになるでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1000031034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.0817730943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nぜひ、そのオススメの車も見せていただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5126381013,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5350.405496899981,
          "startTime": 148.8630435982
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.3630425969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……これがその、イチオシの中古車ですか\n随分年代物のようですし、カスタムもされていますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2963757077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8603226383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "ふむ……他の車と比べても、十分大きいですね\nその分、車内はゆったりしていそうですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5000031034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.955583481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "車高が低いですし、エアロパーツが張り出していますね\nちょっと、自走するチリトリにも見えますね……ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9000031034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.7654475252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（この車の前の持ち主って、どう考えても）\n（昔の……昭和末期の暴走族とか、そんな人だよな！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7658586259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（まさか令和までこんな車が生き残っていたとは）\n（さすがにこれは、mihoさんでも手を出さないだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
